title: Cannot See my Club that I am the leader of
body:
I cannot see my club that I am the owner of in game even though it says I am still in it. The club name is Gnome Lives Matter.

Thank You

replies.body:
Seems we missed you when we rolled out the fixes to the Clubs issues. If you reach out in a [support ticket](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/requests/new) with your club name and tag, we'll work together to resolve this.

Let me know if you have any questions.
